Acquisition notes: Robert Curzon purchased EA 66415 at "Thebes" between January and 9 February 1838 (Muhs and Vorderstrasse JEA 2008. In 1876, Robert Curzon's collection was placed on deposit in the Department of Manuscripts by his son Robin Curzon. Upon her death in 1917, his sister, Darea Curzon, bequeathed the collection the to the British Museum.
